query.sfwSql: SELECT * FROM SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL EPD LEFT JOIN SGT_PLAN P ON EPD.plan_id = P.plan_id LEFT JOIN SGT_PERSON PER ON EPD.person_id = PER.person_id
SELECT * FROM SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER EPH Left outer join sgt_organization org on org.org_id = eph.org_id WHERE EPD.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER_ID=EPH.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER_ID
SELECT MESSAGE_ID,DISPLAY_MESSAGE FROM SGS_MESSAGES WHERE MESSAGE_ID IN (SELECT DISTINCT MESSAGE_ID FROM SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ERROR) order by DISPLAY_MESSAGE
SELECT * FROM SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ERROR EPDERR WHERE EPDERR.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ID=EPD.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ID
SELECT * FROM SGT_PERSON PER WHERE PER.PERSON_ID=EPD.PERSON_ID

select count(1) from sgt_employer_payroll_detail sepd WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN sgt_employer_payroll_header seph WITH(NOLOCK) on sepd.employer_payroll_header_id = seph.employer_payroll_header_id where sepd.person_id = @person_id and seph.org_id = @org_id and sepd.pay_period_date =@pay_period_date and sepd.record_type_value=@record_type and sepd.status_value != 'IGNR' and sepd.plan_id = @planId and EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ID != @empPayDetailId

select count(1) from sgt_employer_payroll_detail sepd inner join sgt_employer_payroll_header seph on sepd.employer_payroll_header_id = seph.employer_payroll_header_id where sepd.person_id = @person_id and seph.org_id = @org_id and sepd.pay_period_start_date =@pay_period_start_date and sepd.record_type_value=@record_type and sepd.status_value != 'IGNR' and sepd.plan_id = @planId and EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ID != @empPayDetailId
delete from sgt_employer_payroll_detail_error where employer_payroll_detail_id = @employer_payroll_detail_id
select isnull(Sum(PAY_PERIOD_CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT),0) from sgt_person_account_deferred_comp_contribution where PAID_DATE between @start_date and @end_date and person_account_id = @Person_account_id

DECLARE @ORGID INT IF(@ORGCODE IS NULL OR @ORGCODE = '') BEGIN SET @ORGID = 0 END ELSE BEGIN SELECT @ORGID = ORG_ID FROM SGT_ORGANIZATION WHERE ORG_CODE = @ORGCODE END IF EXISTS(SELECT '0' FROM SGT_ORG_PLAN A INNER JOIN SGT_PLAN B ON A.PLAN_ID = B.PLAN_ID WHERE ORG_ID = CASE WHEN @ORGID = 0 THEN ORG_ID ELSE @ORGID END AND B.RETIREMENT_TYPE_VALUE IN ('DB','DC','HB') AND ((A.PARTICIPATION_START_DATE <= @START_DATE AND (A.PARTICIPATION_END_DATE IS NULL OR A.PARTICIPATION_END_DATE >= @START_DATE)) OR (A.PARTICIPATION_START_DATE <= @END_DATE AND (A.PARTICIPATION_END_DATE IS NULL OR A.PARTICIPATION_END_DATE >= @END_DATE)) OR (@START_DATE <= A.PARTICIPATION_START_DATE AND @END_DATE >= A.PARTICIPATION_START_DATE) OR (A.PARTICIPATION_END_DATE IS NOT NULL AND @START_DATE <= A.PARTICIPATION_END_DATE AND @END_DATE >= A.PARTICIPATION_END_DATE))) BEGIN SELECT A.*,ISNULL(B.ADDR_LINE_1,'')+', '+ISNULL(B.ADDR_LINE_2,'') AS ADD_L1,ISNULL(B.ADDR_LINE_2,'') AS ADD_L2, ISNULL(B.CITY,'')+', '+ISNULL(CV1.DESCRIPTION,'')+', '+ISNULL(B.ZIP_CODE,'') AS ADD_L3, 'Following is a schedule of contributions reported for the period '+ CONVERT(VARCHAR, @START_DATE, 101) +' to '+ CONVERT(VARCHAR, @END_DATE, 101) +' for '+ A.ORG_NAME+ '.
The sample disclosures that incorporate the new reporting requirements for GASB 68 are located on the NDPERS website. They can be found using this link:

https://ndpers.nd.gov/employers/employer-resources/governmental-accounting-standards-board-gasb/

If you have any further questions or need additional time periods, please contact us.' AS FOOTER_NOTE FROM ( SELECT ORG.ORG_NAME,PL.PLAN_NAME,ORG.ORG_CODE, SUM(CASE WHEN DETL.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE = '-ADJ' THEN -1*DETL.EE_CONTRIBUTION_REPORTED ELSE DETL.EE_CONTRIBUTION_REPORTED END) AS EE_CONTRIBUTION_REPORTED, SUM(CASE WHEN DETL.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE = '-ADJ' THEN -1*DETL.EE_PRE_TAX_REPORTED ELSE DETL.EE_PRE_TAX_REPORTED END) AS EE_PRE_TAX_REPORTED, SUM(CASE WHEN DETL.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE = '-ADJ' THEN -1*DETL.EE_EMPLOYER_PICKUP_REPORTED ELSE DETL.EE_EMPLOYER_PICKUP_REPORTED END) AS EE_EMPLOYER_PICKUP_REPORTED, SUM(CASE WHEN DETL.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE = '-ADJ' THEN -1*DETL.ER_CONTRIBUTION_REPORTED ELSE DETL.ER_CONTRIBUTION_REPORTED END) AS ER_CONTRIBUTION_REPORTED, SUM(CASE WHEN DETL.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE = '-ADJ' THEN -1*DETL.RHIC_ER_CONTRIBUTION_REPORTED ELSE DETL.RHIC_ER_CONTRIBUTION_REPORTED END) AS RHIC_ER_CONTRIBUTION_REPORTED, SUM(CASE WHEN DETL.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE = '-ADJ' THEN -1*DETL.RHIC_EE_CONTRIBUTION_REPORTED ELSE DETL.RHIC_EE_CONTRIBUTION_REPORTED END) AS RHIC_EE_CONTRIBUTION_REPORTED, SUM(CASE WHEN DETL.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE = '-ADJ' THEN -1*DETL.ELIGIBLE_WAGES ELSE DETL.ELIGIBLE_WAGES END) AS ELIGIBLE_WAGES, SUM(CASE WHEN DETL.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE = '-ADJ' THEN -1*DETL.MEMBER_INTEREST_CALCULATED ELSE DETL.MEMBER_INTEREST_CALCULATED END) AS MEMBER_INTEREST_CALCULATED, SUM(CASE WHEN DETL.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE = '-ADJ' THEN -1*DETL.EMPLOYER_INTEREST_CALCULATED ELSE DETL.EMPLOYER_INTEREST_CALCULATED END) AS EMPLOYER_INTEREST_CALCULATED, SUM(CASE WHEN DETL.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE = '-ADJ' THEN -1*DETL.EE_PRETAX_ADDL_REPORTED ELSE DETL.EE_PRETAX_ADDL_REPORTED END) AS EE_PRETAX_ADDL_REPORTED, SUM(CASE WHEN DETL.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE = '-ADJ' THEN -1*DETL.EE_POST_TAX_ADDL_REPORTED ELSE DETL.EE_POST_TAX_ADDL_REPORTED END) AS EE_POST_TAX_ADDL_REPORTED, SUM(CASE WHEN DETL.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE = '-ADJ' THEN -1*DETL.ER_PRETAX_MATCH_REPORTED ELSE DETL.ER_PRETAX_MATCH_REPORTED END) AS ER_PRETAX_MATCH_REPORTED, SUM(CASE WHEN DETL.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE = '-ADJ' THEN -1*DETL.ADEC_REPORTED ELSE DETL.ADEC_REPORTED END) AS ADEC_REPORTED, ORG.PRIMARY_ADDRESS_ID FROM SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER HEAD WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL DETL WITH(NOLOCK) ON DETL.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER_ID = HEAD.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN SGT_PLAN PL WITH(NOLOCK) ON DETL.PLAN_ID = PL.PLAN_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN SGT_ORGANIZATION ORG WITH(NOLOCK) ON HEAD.ORG_ID = ORG.ORG_ID WHERE HEAD.STATUS_VALUE = 'PSTD' and PL.RETIREMENT_TYPE_VALUE in ('DB','DC','HB') AND ORG.ORG_ID = CASE WHEN @ORGID = 0 THEN ORG.ORG_ID ELSE @ORGID END AND DETL.PAY_PERIOD_DATE >= @START_DATE AND DETL.PAY_PERIOD_DATE <= @END_DATE AND ISNULL(DETL.STATUS_VALUE,'') <> 'IGNR' GROUP BY ORG.ORG_NAME,PL.PLAN_NAME,ORG.PRIMARY_ADDRESS_ID,ORG.ORG_CODE ) A INNER JOIN SGT_ORG_CONTACT_ADDRESS B ON A.PRIMARY_ADDRESS_ID = B.CONTACT_ORG_ADDRESS_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE CV1 ON B.STATE_ID = CV1.CODE_ID AND B.STATE_VALUE = CV1.CODE_VALUE --LEFT OUTER JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE CV2 -- ON B.COUNTRY_ID = CV2.CODE_ID AND B.COUNTRY_VALUE = CV2.CODE_VALUE WHERE B.STATUS_VALUE = 'ACTV' END ELSE BEGIN SELECT TOP 1 NULL AS ORG_NAME,NULL AS PLAN_NAME,'-999' AS ORG_CODE, NULL AS EE_CONTRIBUTION_REPORTED, NULL AS EE_PRE_TAX_REPORTED, NULL AS EE_EMPLOYER_PICKUP_REPORTED, NULL AS ER_CONTRIBUTION_REPORTED, NULL AS RHIC_ER_CONTRIBUTION_REPORTED, NULL AS RHIC_EE_CONTRIBUTION_REPORTED, NULL AS ELIGIBLE_WAGES, NULL AS MEMBER_INTEREST_CALCULATED, NULL AS EMPLOYER_INTEREST_CALCULATED, NULL AS PRIMARY_ADDRESS_ID,NULL AS ADD_L1,NULL AS ADD_L2,NULL AS ADD_L3,NULL AS FOOTER_NOTE FROM SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER END
select top 1 effective_date from sgt_person_account_retirement_contribution where subsystem_value = 'INTR' order by effective_date desc

SELECT * FROM SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER EPH INNER JOIN SGT_ORGANIZATION ORG ON ORG.ORG_ID = EPH.ORG_ID INNER JOIN SGT_ORG_CONTACT OC ON OC.ORG_ID=EPH.ORG_ID INNER JOIN SGT_ORG_CONTACT_ROLE OCR ON OCR.ORG_CONTACT_ID = OC.ORG_CONTACT_ID WHERE EPH.ORG_ID = OC.ORG_ID AND isnull(EPD.PLAN_ID,0) = CASE WHEN (OCR.CONTACT_ROLE_VALUE IN ('PAAG', 'AUTH') OR EPH.HEADER_TYPE_VALUE = 'PRCH') THEN isnull(EPD.PLAN_ID,0) ELSE OC.PLAN_ID END AND EPD.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER_ID=EPH.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER_ID

SELECT EPH.HEADER_TYPE_ID, EPH.SUBMITTED_DATE, EPH.HEADER_TYPE_VALUE, CASE WHEN EPD.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE = '-ADJ' THEN EPD.ELIGIBLE_WAGES * -1 ELSE EPD.ELIGIBLE_WAGES END AS ELIGIBLE_WAGES, CASE WHEN EPD.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE = '-ADJ' THEN EPD.EE_CONTRIBUTION_CALCULATED * -1 ELSE EPD.EE_CONTRIBUTION_CALCULATED END AS EE_CONTRIBUTION_CALCULATED, CASE WHEN EPD.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE = '-ADJ' THEN EPD.EE_PRE_TAX_CALCULATED * -1 ELSE EPD.EE_PRE_TAX_CALCULATED END AS EE_PRE_TAX_CALCULATED, CASE WHEN EPD.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE = '-ADJ' THEN EPD.EE_EMPLOYER_PICKUP_CALCULATED * -1 ELSE EPD.EE_EMPLOYER_PICKUP_CALCULATED END AS EE_EMPLOYER_PICKUP_CALCULATED, CASE WHEN EPD.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE = '-ADJ' THEN EPD.RHIC_EE_CONTRIBUTION_CALCULATED * -1 ELSE EPD.RHIC_EE_CONTRIBUTION_CALCULATED END AS RHIC_EE_CONTRIBUTION_CALCULATED, CASE WHEN EPD.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE = '-ADJ' THEN EPD.ER_CONTRIBUTION_CALCULATED * -1 ELSE EPD.ER_CONTRIBUTION_CALCULATED END AS ER_CONTRIBUTION_CALCULATED, CASE WHEN EPD.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE = '-ADJ' THEN EPD.RHIC_ER_CONTRIBUTION_CALCULATED * -1 ELSE EPD.RHIC_ER_CONTRIBUTION_CALCULATED END AS RHIC_ER_CONTRIBUTION_CALCULATED, CASE WHEN EPD.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE = '-ADJ' THEN EPD.MEMBER_INTEREST_CALCULATED * -1 ELSE EPD.MEMBER_INTEREST_CALCULATED END AS MEMBER_INTEREST_CALCULATED, CASE WHEN EPD.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE = '-ADJ' THEN EPD.EMPLOYER_INTEREST_CALCULATED * -1 ELSE EPD.EMPLOYER_INTEREST_CALCULATED END AS EMPLOYER_INTEREST_CALCULATED, CASE WHEN EPD.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE = '-ADJ' THEN EPD.EMPLOYER_RHIC_INTEREST_CALCULATED * -1 ELSE EPD.EMPLOYER_RHIC_INTEREST_CALCULATED END AS EMPLOYER_RHIC_INTEREST_CALCULATED, CASE WHEN EPD.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE = '-ADJ' THEN EPD.PREMIUM_AMOUNT * -1 ELSE EPD.PREMIUM_AMOUNT END AS PREMIUM_AMOUNT, CASE WHEN EPD.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE = '-ADJ' THEN EPD.CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT1 * -1 ELSE EPD.CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT1 END AS CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT1, CASE WHEN EPD.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE = '-ADJ' THEN EPD.CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT2 * -1 ELSE EPD.CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT2 END AS CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT2, CASE WHEN EPD.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE = '-ADJ' THEN EPD.CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT3 * -1 ELSE EPD.CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT3 END AS CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT3, CASE WHEN EPD.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE = '-ADJ' THEN EPD.CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT4 * -1 ELSE EPD.CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT4 END AS CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT4, CASE WHEN EPD.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE = '-ADJ' THEN EPD.CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT5 * -1 ELSE EPD.CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT5 END AS CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT5, CASE WHEN EPD.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE = '-ADJ' THEN EPD.CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT6 * -1 ELSE EPD.CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT6 END AS CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT6, CASE WHEN EPD.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE = '-ADJ' THEN EPD.CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT7 * -1 ELSE EPD.CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT7 END AS CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT7, CASE WHEN EPD.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE = '-ADJ' THEN EPD.PURCHASE_AMOUNT_REPORTED * -1 ELSE EPD.PURCHASE_AMOUNT_REPORTED END AS PURCHASE_AMOUNT_REPORTED, EPD.*, P.*, ORGANIZATION.*, CASE WHEN EPD.PAY_PERIOD_DATE IS NULL THEN '' ELSE RIGHT('00' + CAST(DATEPART(M, EPD.PAY_PERIOD_DATE) AS VARCHAR(2)),2) + '/' + CAST(DATEPART(YYYY, EPD.PAY_PERIOD_DATE) AS VARCHAR(4)) END AS PAY_PERIOD ,
CASE WHEN EPD.PAY_PERIOD_END_MONTH_FOR_BONUS IS NULL THEN '' ELSE RIGHT('00' + CAST(DATEPART(M, EPD.PAY_PERIOD_END_MONTH_FOR_BONUS) AS VARCHAR(2)),2) + '/' + CAST(DATEPART(YYYY, EPD.PAY_PERIOD_END_MONTH_FOR_BONUS) AS VARCHAR(4)) END AS PAY_END_MONTH, PER.PEOPLESOFT_ID AS istrPeopleSoftID FROM SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER EPH WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL EPD WITH(NOLOCK) ON EPH.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER_ID = EPD.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER_ID LEFT JOIN SGT_PLAN P WITH(NOLOCK) ON EPD.PLAN_ID = P.PLAN_ID LEFT JOIN SGT_PERSON PER WITH(NOLOCK) ON EPD.PERSON_ID = PER.PERSON_ID INNER JOIN SGT_ORGANIZATION ORGANIZATION WITH(NOLOCK) ON ORGANIZATION.ORG_ID = EPH.ORG_ID where (1=(case when EPH.HEADER_TYPE_VALUE = 'INSR' and EPD.STATUS_VALUE = 'IGNR' THEN 2 ELSE 1 END)) ORDER BY EPD.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ID DESC

SELECT * FROM ( SELECT Distinct EPD.*,OC.CONTACT_ID,EPH.ORG_ID,EPH.HEADER_TYPE_VALUE,EPH.REPORTING_SOURCE_VALUE FROM SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER EPH Inner Join SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL EPD ON EPH.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER_ID = EPD.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER_ID INNER JOIN SGT_ORG_CONTACT OC ON EPH.ORG_ID = OC.ORG_ID INNER JOIN SGT_ORG_CONTACT_ROLE OCR ON OCR.ORG_CONTACT_ID = OC.ORG_CONTACT_ID WHERE EPD.PLAN_ID = CASE WHEN OCR.CONTACT_ROLE_VALUE IN ('PAAG', 'AUTH') THEN EPD.PLAN_ID ELSE OC.PLAN_ID END )EPD

SELECT 1 FROM SGT_ORG_CONTACT OC INNER JOIN SGT_ORG_CONTACT_ROLE OCR ON OCR.ORG_CONTACT_ID = OC.ORG_CONTACT_ID WHERE EPH.ORG_ID = OC.ORG_ID AND isnull(EPD.PLAN_ID,0) = CASE WHEN (OCR.CONTACT_ROLE_VALUE IN ('PAAG', 'AUTH') OR EPH.HEADER_TYPE_VALUE = 'PRCH') THEN isnull(EPD.PLAN_ID,0) ELSE OC.PLAN_ID END

SELECT DISTINCT EMPDTL.* FROM SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL EMPDTL WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER EMPHDR WITH(NOLOCK) ON EMPDTL.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER_ID = EMPHDR.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER_ID LEFT JOIN SGT_REMITTANCE REM WITH(NOLOCK) ON REM.ORG_ID = EMPHDR.ORG_ID LEFT JOIN SGT_DEPOSIT DEP WITH(NOLOCK) ON REM.DEPOSIT_ID = DEP.DEPOSIT_ID WHERE EMPHDR.STATUS_VALUE <> 'IGNR' AND BALANCING_STATUS_VALUE = 'NOR' AND DEP.STATUS_VALUE IN ('APLD','VALD') AND REM.REMITTANCE_ID IS NOT NULL AND EMPHDR.HEADER_TYPE_VALUE NOT IN ('RETR','INSR') --PROD PIR 6062

SELECT A.* FROM SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL A WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER B WITH(NOLOCK) ON A.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER_ID = B.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER_ID AND B.HEADER_TYPE_VALUE = 'RETR' WHERE A.STATUS_VALUE NOT IN ('PSTD','IGNR') AND A.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE NOT IN ('BONS','NBON') AND A.PERSON_ID IS NOT NULL AND A.PLAN_ID IS NOT NULL AND A.PAY_PERIOD_DATE <= @PAYPERIODDATE

SELECT DISTINCT B.* FROM SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL A WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER B WITH(NOLOCK) ON A.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER_ID = B.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER_ID AND B.HEADER_TYPE_VALUE = 'RETR' WHERE A.STATUS_VALUE NOT IN ('PSTD','IGNR') AND B.STATUS_VALUE NOT IN ('PSTD','IGNR') AND A.PERSON_ID IS NOT NULL AND A.PLAN_ID IS NOT NULL

SELECT ISNULL(SUM(BASIC_PREMIUM),0) as BasicSum, ISNULL(SUM(SUPPLEMENTAL_PREMIUM),0) as SupplementalSum, ISNULL(SUM(SPOUSE_PREMIUM),0)as SpouseSum, ISNULL(SUM(DEPENDENT_PREMIUM),0) as DependentSum FROM SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL(NOLOCK) WHERE EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ID IN (SELECT MAX(EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ID) FROM SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL(NOLOCK) WHERE PLAN_ID=13 AND EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER_ID=@HEADERID GROUP BY EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER_ID,PERSON_ID HAVING COUNT(PERSON_ID)>1 UNION ALL SELECT EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ID FROM SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL(NOLOCK) WHERE PERSON_ID NOT IN (SELECT PERSON_ID FROM SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL(NOLOCK) WHERE PLAN_ID=13 AND EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER_ID=@HEADERID GROUP BY EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER_ID,PERSON_ID HAVING COUNT(PERSON_ID)>1) AND PLAN_ID=13 AND EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER_ID=@HEADERID )

SELECT EPD.*,ORG.ORG_CODE,ORG_NAME,P.PLAN_NAME, CASE WHEN EPD.PAY_PERIOD_DATE IS NULL THEN '' ELSE right('00' + Cast(DATEPART(M, EPD.PAY_PERIOD_DATE) as varchar(2)),2) + '/' + cast(DATEPART(yyyy, EPD.PAY_PERIOD_DATE) as varchar(4)) END AS PAY_PERIOD ,
CASE WHEN EPD.PAY_PERIOD_END_MONTH_FOR_BONUS IS NULL THEN '' ELSE right('00' + Cast(DATEPART(M, EPD.PAY_PERIOD_END_MONTH_FOR_BONUS) as varchar(2)),2) + '/' + cast(DATEPART(yyyy, EPD.PAY_PERIOD_END_MONTH_FOR_BONUS) as varchar(4)) END AS pay_end_month,PER.PEOPLESOFT_ID AS istrPeopleSoftID FROM SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL EPD INNER JOIN SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER EPH ON EPH.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER_ID = EPD.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER_ID INNER JOIN SGT_ORGANIZATION ORG ON ORG.ORG_ID = EPH.ORG_ID LEFT JOIN SGT_PLAN P ON EPD.PLAN_ID = P.PLAN_ID LEFT JOIN SGT_PERSON PER WITH(NOLOCK) ON EPD.PERSON_ID = PER.PERSON_ID ORDER BY EPD.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ID DESC

DECLARE @LASTFIRSTPAYPERIODMONTH INT = (SELECT MONTH(DATEADD(MONTH, -1, @PAYPERIODLASTDATE))) DECLARE @LASTFIRSTPAYPERIODYEAR INT = (SELECT YEAR(DATEADD(MONTH, -1, @PAYPERIODLASTDATE))) DECLARE @LASTSECONDPAYPERIODMONTH INT = (SELECT MONTH(DATEADD(MONTH, -2, @PAYPERIODLASTDATE))) DECLARE @LASTSECONDPAYPERIODYEAR INT = (SELECT YEAR(DATEADD(MONTH, -2, @PAYPERIODLASTDATE)))
SELECT PARC.PAY_PERIOD_MONTH, PARC.PAY_PERIOD_YEAR, SUM(ISNULL(PARC.SALARY_AMOUNT, 0)) AS OLD_SALARY_AMOUNT FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_RETIREMENT_CONTRIBUTION PARC WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_EMPLOYMENT_DETAIL PED WITH(NOLOCK) ON PARC.PERSON_EMPLOYMENT_DTL_ID = PED.PERSON_EMPLOYMENT_DTL_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_EMPLOYMENT PE WITH(NOLOCK) ON PE.PERSON_EMPLOYMENT_ID = PED.PERSON_EMPLOYMENT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL EPD WITH(NOLOCK) ON EPD.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ID = PARC.SUBSYSTEM_REF_ID WHERE PARC.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = @PERSONACCOUNTID AND PE.ORG_ID = @ORGID AND PARC.TRANSACTION_TYPE_VALUE IN ('RGPR', 'PRAD') AND EPD.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE NOT IN ('BONS','NBON') GROUP BY PARC.PAY_PERIOD_MONTH, PARC.PAY_PERIOD_YEAR HAVING (PARC.PAY_PERIOD_MONTH = @LASTFIRSTPAYPERIODMONTH AND PARC.PAY_PERIOD_YEAR = @LASTFIRSTPAYPERIODYEAR AND SUM(ISNULL(PARC.SALARY_AMOUNT, 0)) >0) OR (PARC.PAY_PERIOD_MONTH = @LASTSECONDPAYPERIODMONTH AND PARC.PAY_PERIOD_YEAR = @LASTSECONDPAYPERIODYEAR AND SUM(ISNULL(PARC.SALARY_AMOUNT, 0))>0) ORDER BY PARC.PAY_PERIOD_YEAR DESC, PARC.PAY_PERIOD_MONTH DESC

declare @FinalPlan_ID varchar(max) = case when @ddlPlan is null or @ddlPlan = '' then @ALL_PLAN_ID else @ddlPlan end SELECT C.ORG_CODE , B.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER_ID , A.PERSON_ID AS PERSLINK_ID , A.PLAN_ID = 7 THEN 'DEFINED CONTRIBUTION' WHEN A.PLAN_ID = 28 THEN 'DEFINED CONTRIBUTION 2020' WHEN A.PLAN_ID = 30 THEN 'DEFINED CONTRIBUTION 2025' WHEN A.PLAN_ID = 4 THEN 'HIGHWAY PATROL' WHEN A.PLAN_ID = 19 THEN 'DEFERRED COMPENSATION' WHEN A.PLAN_ID = 3 THEN 'NATIONAL GUARD' END AS PLAN_NAME , A.RECORD_TYPE_VALUE , case when ISNULL(DATEPART(MM,B.PAYROLL_PAID_DATE),' ') is null then ' ' else DATEPART(MM,B.PAYROLL_PAID_DATE) end AS REPORTING_MONTH, case when ISNULL(DATEPART(YYYY,B.PAYROLL_PAID_DATE),'') is null then ' 'else DATEPART(YYYY,B.PAYROLL_PAID_DATE) end AS REPORTING_YEAR, ISNULL(A.EE_CONTRIBUTION_CALCULATED, 0) AS EE_CONTRIBUTION_CALCULATED , ISNULL(A.EE_PRE_TAX_CALCULATED, 0) AS EE_PRE_TAX_CALCULATED , ISNULL(A.EE_EMPLOYER_PICKUP_CALCULATED, 0) AS EE_EMPLOYER_PICKUP_CALCULATED , ISNULL(A.ER_CONTRIBUTION_CALCULATED, 0) AS ER_CONTRIBUTION_CALCULATED , ISNULL(A.RHIC_EE_CONTRIBUTION_CALCULATED, 0) AS RHIC_EE_CONTRIBUTION_CALCULATED , ISNULL(A.RHIC_ER_CONTRIBUTION_CALCULATED, 0) AS RHIC_ER_CONTRIBUTION_CALCULATED , ISNULL(A.ELIGIBLE_WAGES, 0) AS ELIGIBLE_WAGES , B.PAY_PERIOD_START_DATE , B.PAY_PERIOD_END_DATE , ISNULL(A.CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT1, 0) AS CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT1 , ISNULL(A.PROVIDER_ORG_CODE_ID1, '') AS PROVIDER1 , ISNULL(A.CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT2, 0) AS CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT2 , ISNULL(A.PROVIDER_ORG_CODE_ID2, '') AS PROVIDER2 , ISNULL(A.CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT3, 0) AS CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT3 , ISNULL(A.PROVIDER_ORG_CODE_ID3, '') AS PROVIDER3 , ISNULL(A.CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT4, 0) AS CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT4 , ISNULL(A.PROVIDER_ORG_CODE_ID4, '') AS PROVIDER4 , ISNULL(A.CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT5, 0) AS CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT5 , ISNULL(A.PROVIDER_ORG_CODE_ID5, '') AS PROVIDER5 , ISNULL(A.CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT6, 0) AS CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT6 , ISNULL(A.PROVIDER_ORG_CODE_ID6, '') AS PROVIDER6 , ISNULL(A.CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT7, 0) AS CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT7 , ISNULL(A.PROVIDER_ORG_CODE_ID7, '') AS PROVIDER7 , A.POSTED_DATE , ISNULL(A.EE_PRETAX_ADDL_CALCULATED,0) AS EE_PRETAX_ADDL_CALCULATED , ISNULL(A.EE_POST_TAX_ADDL_CALCULATED,0) AS EE_POST_TAX_ADDL_CALCULATED , ISNULL(A.ER_PRETAX_MATCH_CALCULATED,0) AS ER_PRETAX_MATCH_CALCULATED , ISNULL(A.ADEC_CALCULATED,0) AS ADEC_CALCULATED , ISNULL(A.ELIGIBLE_WAGES_DEFCOMP,0) AS SGT_ORGANIZATION C WITH(NOLOCK) ON B.ORG_ID = C.ORG_ID WHERE A.POSTED_DATE BETWEEN @POSTED_DATE_FROM AND @POSTED_DATE_TO AND B.HEADER_TYPE_VALUE IN ('RETR', 'DEFF') AND A.PLAN_ID <> 8 and a.PLAN_ID in SELECT M.MESSAGE_ID, M.DISPLAY_MESSAGE AS istrDisplayMessage, M.DISPLAY_MESSAGE as long_description, CV.DESCRIPTION AS severity_description, M.EMPLOYER_INSTRUCTIONS AS istrEmployerInstructions FROM SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL EPD INNER JOIN SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ERROR EPDE ON EPD.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ID = EPDE.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ID INNER JOIN SGS_MESSAGES M ON EPDE.MESSAGE_ID = M.MESSAGE_ID INNER JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE CV ON M.SEVERITY_ID = CV.CODE_ID AND M.SEVERITY_VALUE = CV.CODE_VALUE WHERE EPDE.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ID = @EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ID AND (M.severity_value = 'E' or M.severity_value = 'W') AND EPD.STATUS_VALUE NOT IN ('PSTD', 'IGNR', 'VALD')
SELECT * FROM SGT_SERVICE_PURCHASE_HEADER where PERSON_ID = @PERSONID and SERVICE_PURCHASE_STATUS_VALUE = 'VALD' and ACTION_STATUS_VALUE = 'INPY'

--DECLARE @EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ID INT = 35420392 DECLARE @EMPLOYERMATCH DECIMAL(13,2), @PAY_PERIOD_CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT DECIMAL(13,2), @DEFERRED_COMP_CONTRIBUTION_ID INT, @NEGATIVEADJUSTMENT INT
IF OBJECT_ID(N'tempdb..#TEMP_PROVIDER_DATA') IS NOT NULL BEGIN DROP TABLE #TEMP_PROVIDER_DATA END SELECT @EMPLOYERMATCH = ER_PRETAX_MATCH_CALCULATED, @NEGATIVEADJUSTMENT = CASE WHEN RECORD_TYPE_VALUE = '-ADJ' OR RECORD_TYPE_VALUE = 'NBON' THEN -1 ELSE 1 END FROM SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL EPD WHERE EPD.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ID = @EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ID SELECT @EMPLOYERMATCH = @EMPLOYERMATCH * @NEGATIVEADJUSTMENT SELECT @PAY_PERIOD_CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT = SUM(DEFFCOMPCONT.PAY_PERIOD_CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT) FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_DEFERRED_COMP_CONTRIBUTION DEFFCOMPCONT WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE DEFFCOMPCONT.SUBSYSTEM_REF_ID = @EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ID
SELECT @EMPLOYERMATCH = CASE WHEN ISNULL(@EMPLOYERMATCH,0.0) < ISNULL(@PAY_PERIOD_CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT,0.0) OR ISNULL(@PAY_PERIOD_CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT,0.0) <= 0.0 THEN @EMPLOYERMATCH ELSE @PAY_PERIOD_CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT END
IF((SELECT COUNT(1) FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_DEFERRED_COMP_CONTRIBUTION WHERE SUBSYSTEM_REF_ID = @EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ID) = 1) BEGIN UPDATE SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_DEFERRED_COMP_CONTRIBUTION SET EMPLOYER_MATCH_AMOUNT = @EMPLOYERMATCH WHERE SUBSYSTEM_REF_ID = @EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ID UPDATE SGT_PROVIDER_REPORT_DATA_DEFF_COMP SET ER_PRETAX_MATCH = @EMPLOYERMATCH WHERE SUBSYSTEM_REF_ID = @EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ID END ELSE IF(@EMPLOYERMATCH <> 0 ) BEGIN SELECT DEFFCOMPCONT.DEFERRED_COMP_CONTRIBUTION_ID, DEFFCOMPCONT.PAY_PERIOD_CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT,EMPLOYER_MATCH_AMOUNT ,CASE WHEN IS_APPLY_EMPLOYER_MATCHING_CONTRIBUTION = 'Y' THEN 0 ELSE DATEDIFF(DD, DEFPROVIDER.START_DATE , ISNULL(DEFPROVIDER.END_DATE,'12/13/9999')) END AS PROVIDR_SEQ INTO #TEMP_PROVIDER_DATA FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_DEFERRED_COMP_CONTRIBUTION DEFFCOMPCONT WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_ORGANIZATION O WITH(NOLOCK) ON O.ORG_ID = DEFFCOMPCONT.PROVIDER_ORG_ID INNER JOIN SGT_ORG_PLAN OP WITH(NOLOCK) ON OP.ORG_ID = O.ORG_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_DEFERRED_COMP_PROVIDER DEFPROVIDER WITH(NOLOCK) ON DEFPROVIDER.PROVIDER_ORG_PLAN_ID = OP.ORG_PLAN_ID AND DEFPROVIDER.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = DEFFCOMPCONT.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID AND DEFFCOMPCONT.PAY_PERIOD_END_DATE BETWEEN DEFPROVIDER.START_DATE AND COALESCE(DEFPROVIDER.END_DATE,DEFFCOMPCONT.PAY_PERIOD_END_DATE) --INNER JOIN SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL EPD ON EPD.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ID = DEFFCOMPCONT.SUBSYSTEM_REF_ID WHERE SUBSYSTEM_REF_ID = @EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ID
UPDATE #TEMP_PROVIDER_DATA SET PROVIDR_SEQ = (SELECT MAX(PROVIDR_SEQ) + 1 FROM #TEMP_PROVIDER_DATA) WHERE PROVIDR_SEQ = 0
SELECT TOP 1 @DEFERRED_COMP_CONTRIBUTION_ID = DEFERRED_COMP_CONTRIBUTION_ID FROM #TEMP_PROVIDER_DATA ORDER BY PROVIDR_SEQ DESC
UPDATE SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_DEFERRED_COMP_CONTRIBUTION SET EMPLOYER_MATCH_AMOUNT = @EMPLOYERMATCH WHERE DEFERRED_COMP_CONTRIBUTION_ID = @DEFERRED_COMP_CONTRIBUTION_ID UPDATE SGT_PROVIDER_REPORT_DATA_DEFF_COMP SET ER_PRETAX_MATCH = @EMPLOYERMATCH WHERE SUBSYSTEM_REF_ID = @EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ID AND PROVIDER_ORG_ID = (SELECT TOP 1 PROVIDER_ORG_ID FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_DEFERRED_COMP_CONTRIBUTION WHERE DEFERRED_COMP_CONTRIBUTION_ID = @DEFERRED_COMP_CONTRIBUTION_ID ) END

SELECT * FROM SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER EPH WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL EPD WITH(NOLOCK) ON EPD.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER_ID = EPH.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER_ID WHERE EPD.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND EPH.HEADER_TYPE_VALUE = 'DEFF' AND EPH.STATUS_VALUE = 'PSTD' AND EPD.STATUS_VALUE = 'PSTD' AND EPD.CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT1 IS NOT NULL AND EPD.PROVIDER_ID1 IS NOT NULL AND ((@EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ID = 0 AND @ORG_id <> EPH.ORG_ID) OR EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER EPHIN WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL EPDIN WITH(NOLOCK) ON EPDIN.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER_ID = EPHIN.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_HEADER_ID WHERE EPDIN.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ID = @EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ID AND EPDIN.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND EPHIN.HEADER_TYPE_VALUE = 'DEFF' AND EPDIN.PAY_PERIOD_START_DATE = EPD.PAY_PERIOD_START_DATE AND EPDIN.PAY_PERIOD_END_DATE = EPD.PAY_PERIOD_END_DATE AND EPHIN.ORG_ID <> EPH.ORG_ID ) )

SELECT M.MESSAGE_ID, M.DISPLAY_MESSAGE AS istrDisplayMessage, M.DISPLAY_MESSAGE as long_description, CV.DESCRIPTION AS severity_description, M.EMPLOYER_MESSAGE_DESCRIPTION AS istrEmployerMessageDescription FROM SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL EPD INNER JOIN SGT_EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ERROR EPDE ON EPD.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ID = EPDE.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ID INNER JOIN SGS_MESSAGES M ON EPDE.MESSAGE_ID = M.MESSAGE_ID INNER JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE CV ON M.SEVERITY_ID = CV.CODE_ID AND M.SEVERITY_VALUE = CV.CODE_VALUE WHERE EPDE.EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ID = @EMPLOYER_PAYROLL_DETAIL_ID AND (M.severity_value = 'E' or M.severity_value = 'W') AND EPD.STATUS_VALUE NOT IN ('PSTD', 'IGNR', 'VALD')

SELECT 1 FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT PA WITH(NOLOCK) JOIN SGT_PLAN P WITH(NOLOCK) ON PA.PERSON_ID = @PERSONID AND PA.PLAN_ID = @PLANID AND P.PLAN_ID = PA.PLAN_ID AND P.BENEFIT_TYPE_VALUE = 'RETR' JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_RETIREMENT_HISTORY H WITH(NOLOCK) ON H.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = PA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID AND H.PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'ENL1'

DECLARE @CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT decimal(18,2) = @TOTALAMOUNT
DECLARE @CODEID INT = CASE WHEN @ISRHIC = 'TRUE' THEN 7037 ELSE 2324 END --IN CODE ID 7037 NO PLAN ID COLUMN BECAUSE FOR ALL PLAN SAME INTEREST RATE
IF @CODEID = 7037 BEGIN SET @PLANID = 0 END
DECLARE @STARTDATE DATETIME = @PAYROLLDATE, @ENDDATE DATETIME , @TOTALCALCULATEDINTERESTAMOUNT DECIMAL(18,2) = 0
SET @ENDDATE = (SELECT TOP 1 CAST(DATA1 AS DATETIME) FROM SGS_CODE_VALUE WHERE CODE_ID = @CODEID AND CAST(DATA1 AS DATETIME) > @PAYMENTDATE AND ISNULL(CAST(DATA3 AS INT),0) = @PLANID ORDER BY CAST(DATA1 AS DATETIME))
SET @ENDDATE = ISNULL(@ENDDATE,@SUBMITTEDDATE)
WHILE(@STARTDATE <= @ENDDATE) BEGIN SELECT CAST(DATA2 AS DECIMAL(9,2)) AS INTPERCENTAGE, CAST(DATA3 AS INT) AS PLAN_ID, RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY CAST(DATA3 AS INT) ORDER BY CAST(DATA1 AS DATETIME) DESC) AS ROWRANK INTO #TEMP FROM SGS_CODE_VALUE WHERE CODE_ID = @CODEID AND CAST(DATA1 AS DATETIME) <= @STARTDATE AND ISNULL(CAST(DATA3 AS INT),0) = @PLANID ORDER BY CAST(DATA1 AS DATETIME) DESC
SELECT INTPERCENTAGE INTO #TEMPRATE FROM #TEMP WHERE ROWRANK = 1
DECLARE @DAYSINTERVAL INT SELECT @DAYSINTERVAL = DATEDIFF(D, @STARTDATE, @ENDDATE)
IF(@DAYSINTERVAL < 0) BEGIN SET @DAYSINTERVAL = 0 END
DECLARE @CALCULATEDINTERESTAMOUNT DECIMAL(18,2) SET @CALCULATEDINTERESTAMOUNT = (SELECT ROUND(((POWER((1+INTPERCENTAGE/100.0), @DAYSINTERVAL/366.0)* @CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT) - @CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT ),2) FROM #TEMPRATE)
SET @TOTALCALCULATEDINTERESTAMOUNT = @TOTALCALCULATEDINTERESTAMOUNT + @CALCULATEDINTERESTAMOUNT SET @STARTDATE = @ENDDATE SET @ENDDATE = (SELECT TOP 1 CAST(DATA1 AS DATETIME) AS NEXTENDDATE FROM SGS_CODE_VALUE WHERE CODE_ID = @CODEID AND CAST(DATA1 AS DATETIME) > @STARTDATE AND ISNULL(CAST(DATA3 AS INT),0) = @PLANID ORDER BY CAST(DATA1 AS DATETIME))
SET @ENDDATE = ISNULL(@ENDDATE,@SUBMITTEDDATE) SET @CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT = @CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT + @CALCULATEDINTERESTAMOUNT
IF(@ENDDATE = @STARTDATE) BEGIN BREAK END
DROP TABLE #TEMP DROP TABLE #TEMPRATE END
SELECT @TOTALCALCULATEDINTERESTAMOUNT
